Installation instruction for source and binary tar.gz package
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Before install this program please install Raspbian Lite OS to SD-CARD.
Do not forget to set hostname and network and enable SPI module.

Installation
~~~~~~~~~~~~
  $ tar -xzf mm5d-sw-0.1-armhf.tar.gz
  $ cd mm5d-sw
  $ sudo raspi-config
  $ ./prepare
  $ ./install

Set program
~~~~~~~~~~~
  $ mm5d-editmainconf

Set environment characteristics
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
  $ mm5d-editenvirconf

Removing
~~~~~~~~
  $ cd mm5d-sw
  $ ./uninstall
